==Legacy==
''Planet of Zoom'' went on to influence the 1985 Sega game, ''[[Space Harrier]]'', which in turn influenced [[Nintendo]]'s 1993 game, ''[[Star Fox (1993 video game)|Star Fox]]''.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Weiss |first1=Brett Alan |title=Star Fox - Overview |url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=2613 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141206081002/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=2613 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2014-12-06 |website=[[AllGame]] |access-date=5 May 2021 |date=6 December 2014}}</ref>

